Name: biomethane, low pressure burned in solid oxide fuel cell 125kWe, future | heat, future | EN15804GD, U
Category: D:Electricity, gas, steam and air conditioning supply/35:Electricity, gas, steam and air conditioning supply
Description: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with unpressurised tubular stack design for central cogeneration use. Performance, stack lifetime and catalyst use according to expected future values for a serial product. Operation with refined biogas from low pressure gas network. Electrical efficiency 47%, total efficiency 80%. Operation as base load engine with low partial load hours.
